[SPEAKER_01] I sada se mi vratimo

741
00:35:15,800 --> 00:35:16,099
[SPEAKER_01] ovome.

742
00:35:16,099 --> 00:35:17,179
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, oni su stvorili

743
00:35:17,179 --> 00:35:18,900
[SPEAKER_01] ovu hipermodularnu strukturu.

744
00:35:18,900 --> 00:35:21,219
[SPEAKER_01] Desetak, čak tri su

745
00:35:21,219 --> 00:35:22,139
[SPEAKER_01] bila negdje vojni,

746
00:35:22,139 --> 00:35:23,380
[SPEAKER_01] ali su izvednici.

747
00:35:23,380 --> 00:35:25,280
[SPEAKER_01] Izvednici od diverzanske.

748
00:35:25,280 --> 00:35:27,400
[SPEAKER_01] I što su oni napravili?

749
00:35:27,400 --> 00:35:28,539
[SPEAKER_01] Uvježbali ih.

750
00:35:28,539 --> 00:35:31,360
[SPEAKER_01] Oni su negdje oko

751
00:35:31,360 --> 00:35:32,300
[SPEAKER_01] 20.000

752
00:35:32,300 --> 00:35:33,500
[SPEAKER_01] ukupno snaga imali,

753
00:35:33,500 --> 00:35:34,300
[SPEAKER_01] koja su krenuli

754
00:35:34,300 --> 00:35:35,260
[SPEAKER_01] u Kursku.

755
00:35:35,260 --> 00:35:36,039
[SPEAKER_01] Govorite o Ukrajnicima.

756
00:35:36,039 --> 00:35:37,039
[SPEAKER_01] napraviti o Ukrajini.

757
00:35:37,039 --> 00:35:37,860
[SPEAKER_01] Govorio je na Ukrajini.

758
00:35:37,860 --> 00:35:40,320
[SPEAKER_01] I te male module,

759
00:35:40,320 --> 00:35:41,699
[SPEAKER_01] one su pustili u prostor.

760
00:35:41,699 --> 00:35:45,159
[SPEAKER_01] Na zapadnim oklopnim vozilima,

761
00:35:45,159 --> 00:35:46,539
[SPEAKER_01] znači brzo prohodnim.

762
00:35:46,539 --> 00:35:51,059
[SPEAKER_01] I zapovjeđeno ime.

763
00:35:51,059 --> 00:35:52,980
[SPEAKER_01] Čak i jedan od tih zapovjednika,

764
00:35:52,980 --> 00:35:54,079
[SPEAKER_01] koje ga su zarobili,

765
00:35:54,079 --> 00:35:54,860
[SPEAKER_01] Rusi priča,

766
00:35:54,860 --> 00:35:56,639
[SPEAKER_01] ovo čemu sad ja ću reći,

767
00:35:56,639 --> 00:35:58,179
[SPEAKER_01] ali prije sam to napisao

768
00:35:58,179 --> 00:35:58,719
[SPEAKER_01] u svojom knjizi,

769
00:35:58,719 --> 00:35:59,199
[SPEAKER_01] suvremeno,

770
00:35:59,199 --> 00:36:00,400
[SPEAKER_01] umijeće ratovanja,

771
00:36:00,400 --> 00:36:01,099
[SPEAKER_01] koja će izići

772
00:36:01,099 --> 00:36:01,920
[SPEAKER_01] nakon ove knjige

773
00:36:01,920 --> 00:36:04,219
[SPEAKER_01] Uzvišena civilizacija

774
00:36:04,219 --> 00:36:05,500
[SPEAKER_01] o Ilirime i Igle Goljice,

775
00:36:05,500 --> 00:36:10,219
[SPEAKER_01] da ne smiju stupiti

776
00:36:10,219 --> 00:36:11,380
[SPEAKER_01] u borbeni kontakt.

777
00:36:11,380 --> 00:36:12,199
[SPEAKER_01] Znači,

778
00:36:12,199 --> 00:36:14,360
[SPEAKER_01] on ima informaciju

779
00:36:14,360 --> 00:36:17,480
[SPEAKER_01] gdje ima zapadne satelite,

780
00:36:17,480 --> 00:36:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] uključujući i maska,

781
00:36:19,000 --> 00:36:20,719
[SPEAKER_01] ima neprekidnu mrežu.

782
00:36:20,719 --> 00:36:22,019
[SPEAKER_01] Sad je ovo pojam mreže,

783
00:36:22,019 --> 00:36:22,840
[SPEAKER_01] to je sad pitno.

784
00:36:22,840 --> 00:36:25,219
[SPEAKER_01] Ima mrežu gdje je neprekidno

785
00:36:25,219 --> 00:36:26,599
[SPEAKER_01] u realnom vremenu,

786
00:36:26,599 --> 00:36:28,280
[SPEAKER_01] odnosno u kiperrealnom vrijeme,

787
00:36:28,280 --> 00:36:29,780
[SPEAKER_01] a kiperrealno vrijeme je nula.

788
00:36:30,860 --> 00:36:32,360
[SPEAKER_01] U vojnom umijeću

789
00:36:32,360 --> 00:36:33,739
[SPEAKER_01] realno vrijeme može biti

790
00:36:33,739 --> 00:36:35,119
[SPEAKER_01] jedan sat pomaknut.

791
00:36:35,119 --> 00:36:36,619
[SPEAKER_01] Ali je realno vrijeme,

792
00:36:36,619 --> 00:36:37,239
[SPEAKER_01] jer može brzo,

793
00:36:37,239 --> 00:36:38,179
[SPEAKER_01] jer je glavni,

794
00:36:38,179 --> 00:36:40,139
[SPEAKER_01] jer to je rat četvrte dimenzije,

795
00:36:40,139 --> 00:36:41,139
[SPEAKER_01] jer je to,

796
00:36:41,139 --> 00:36:43,320
[SPEAKER_01] a glavni geslo,

797
00:36:43,320 --> 00:36:44,820
[SPEAKER_01] to ga je otkri,

798
00:36:44,820 --> 00:36:45,880
[SPEAKER_01] odluči i uništi.

799
00:36:45,880 --> 00:36:47,539
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, vrlo brzo odjedno.

800
00:36:47,539 --> 00:36:48,079
[SPEAKER_00] Sada.

801
00:36:48,079 --> 00:36:49,059
[SPEAKER_01] Sada, e.

802
00:36:49,059 --> 00:36:50,739
[SPEAKER_01] I to može do sat vremena,

803
00:36:50,739 --> 00:36:52,139
[SPEAKER_01] jer to resimo realno vrijeme.

804
00:36:52,139 --> 00:36:53,300
[SPEAKER_01] Međutim, u ovome slučaju

805
00:36:53,300 --> 00:36:54,940
[SPEAKER_01] se radilo o kiperrealnom vremenu

806
00:36:54,940 --> 00:36:55,840
[SPEAKER_01] ili vremenu nulu.

807
00:36:55,840 --> 00:36:56,800
[SPEAKER_01] Naime, o čemu je riječ?

808
00:36:56,800 --> 00:36:58,400
[SPEAKER_01] Zapovjednik te desetine

809
00:36:58,400 --> 00:37:00,760
[SPEAKER_01] je imao informaciju

810
00:37:00,760 --> 00:37:02,699
[SPEAKER_01] sa svih mogućih satelita,

811
00:37:02,699 --> 00:37:03,719
[SPEAKER_01] integrirani,

812
00:37:03,719 --> 00:37:06,380
[SPEAKER_01] u kojem siljeve i puteve

813
00:37:06,380 --> 00:37:08,059
[SPEAKER_01] određuje umjetna inteligencija

814
00:37:08,059 --> 00:37:09,960
[SPEAKER_01] na način po kojem

815
00:37:09,960 --> 00:37:11,320
[SPEAKER_01] kad se vozi auto,

816
00:37:11,320 --> 00:37:11,800
[SPEAKER_01] dajete,

817
00:37:11,800 --> 00:37:12,900
[SPEAKER_01] skreni ovdje,

818
00:37:12,900 --> 00:37:14,099
[SPEAKER_01] ovdje toliko ima,

819
00:37:14,099 --> 00:37:14,960
[SPEAKER_01] tako i tu.

820
00:37:15,119 --> 00:37:17,119
[SPEAKER_00] I onda te veze u krivi.

821
00:37:17,119 --> 00:37:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] I onda te vodi kroz šume,

822
00:37:18,000 --> 00:37:18,619
[SPEAKER_01] šumarke,

823
00:37:18,619 --> 00:37:19,500
[SPEAKER_01] ovo i ostaloga,

824
00:37:19,500 --> 00:37:22,199
[SPEAKER_01] da ti postigne što dublji proudor,

825
00:37:22,199 --> 00:37:23,239
[SPEAKER_01] jer oni su morali

826
00:37:23,239 --> 00:37:25,260
[SPEAKER_01] za sedam dana po njihovom planu

827
00:37:25,260 --> 00:37:27,059
[SPEAKER_01] doći do jednog plana elektranije.

828
00:37:27,059 --> 00:37:29,599
[SPEAKER_01] I sad, ne samo to,

829
00:37:29,599 --> 00:37:31,519
[SPEAKER_01] što omoguće još jedno,

830
00:37:31,519 --> 00:37:34,019
[SPEAKER_01] to je jedan novi doktrinarni fenomen,

831
00:37:34,019 --> 00:37:36,059
[SPEAKER_01] to je fenomen hobotnici.

832
00:37:36,059 --> 00:37:37,639
[SPEAKER_01] Hobotnici ima krakovi,

833
00:37:37,639 --> 00:37:38,019
[SPEAKER_01] tako?

834
00:37:38,019 --> 00:37:39,239
[SPEAKER_01] Osam krakov.

835
00:37:39,239 --> 00:37:41,019
[SPEAKER_01] I sad, svaki krak

836
00:37:41,019 --> 00:37:42,460
[SPEAKER_01] ide neovisno jedno od drugoga,

837
00:37:42,460 --> 00:37:44,300
[SPEAKER_01] možda raditi.

838
00:37:44,300 --> 00:37:45,079
[SPEAKER_01] Tako i ovdje.

839
00:37:45,079 --> 00:37:46,880
[SPEAKER_01] Nema klasičnih pravaca

840
00:37:46,880 --> 00:37:48,460
[SPEAKER_01] koji je bio glavni pravac napada,

841
00:37:48,460 --> 00:37:49,420
[SPEAKER_01] pa jedan ili dva,

842
00:37:49,420 --> 00:37:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] ne znam,

843
00:37:50,000 --> 00:37:51,219
[SPEAKER_01] pomoćna pravac napada.

844
00:37:51,219 --> 00:37:51,559
[SPEAKER_01] Ne.

845
00:37:51,559 --> 00:37:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] Svi su oni glavni

846
00:37:53,000 --> 00:37:54,139
[SPEAKER_01] i svi su oni pomoćni.

847
00:37:54,139 --> 00:37:55,980
[SPEAKER_01] U ovisi,

848
00:37:55,980 --> 00:37:57,539
[SPEAKER_01] jer ga vodi umjetna inteligencija

849
00:37:57,539 --> 00:37:58,980
[SPEAKER_01] da tamo što dublje prodre

850
00:37:58,980 --> 00:38:00,280
[SPEAKER_01] za što kraće vrijeme.

851
00:38:00,280 --> 00:38:02,139
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, svaki taj krak

852
00:38:02,139 --> 00:38:03,340
[SPEAKER_01] djelio neovisno,

853
00:38:03,340 --> 00:38:04,820
[SPEAKER_01] ali svi ti krakovi

854
00:38:04,820 --> 00:38:06,699
[SPEAKER_01] stvore jednu cijelinu.

855
00:38:06,699 --> 00:38:08,719
[SPEAKER_00] To su ta nova doktrinarna načela.

856
00:38:08,719 --> 00:38:10,460
[SPEAKER_01] To su ta nova doktrinarna načela

857
00:38:10,460 --> 00:38:12,599
[SPEAKER_01] koju sam ja napisao u knjizi

858
00:38:12,599 --> 00:38:15,039
[SPEAKER_01] i zove se Rat mreža

859
00:38:15,039 --> 00:38:17,639
[SPEAKER_01] ili vremena jata i rojeva.

860
00:38:17,639 --> 00:38:19,480
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, besplotnih letilica.

861
00:38:19,480 --> 00:38:21,519
[SPEAKER_01] I oni su,

862
00:38:21,519 --> 00:38:23,300
[SPEAKER_01] primjenjući umjetnu inteligenciju,

863
00:38:23,300 --> 00:38:23,960
[SPEAKER_01] uspjeli

864
00:38:23,960 --> 00:38:25,940
[SPEAKER_01] u prva tri dana

865
00:38:25,940 --> 00:38:27,840
[SPEAKER_01] doći do negdje dubine

866
00:38:27,840 --> 00:38:30,320
[SPEAKER_01] 30 i koji kilometar više.

867
00:38:30,320 --> 00:38:31,659
[SPEAKER_01] Neki krake je čak i duže.

868
00:38:31,659 --> 00:38:33,300
[SPEAKER_01] Došao do 40 kilometara,

869
00:38:33,300 --> 00:38:35,199
[SPEAKER_01] ali nije došao do 70.

870
00:38:35,199 --> 00:38:36,880
[SPEAKER_01] A zašto nisu uspjeli?

871
00:38:36,880 --> 00:38:38,099
[SPEAKER_01] E, zato, jer je to mreža.

872
00:38:38,199 --> 00:38:39,880
[SPEAKER_01] što se, o čemu se ovdje rade fenomen.

873
00:38:39,880 --> 00:38:41,940
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, nema više velikih pozrobi,

874
00:38:41,940 --> 00:38:45,019
[SPEAKER_01] nego se te mali moduli,

875
00:38:45,019 --> 00:38:46,659
[SPEAKER_01] zato se zove hipermodularna,

876
00:38:46,659 --> 00:38:48,739
[SPEAKER_01] rasporede što više u prostor.

877
00:38:48,739 --> 00:38:51,219
[SPEAKER_01] Ako vi rasporedite ih u prostor,

878
00:38:51,219 --> 00:38:53,059
[SPEAKER_01] tada su oni neki oblik čvorova,

879
00:38:53,440 --> 00:38:58,179
[SPEAKER_01] a oni su povezani čim komunikacijama u realnom vremenu,

880
00:38:58,179 --> 00:39:00,019
[SPEAKER_01] uključujući umjetnu inteligenciju,

881
00:39:00,019 --> 00:39:01,400
[SPEAKER_01] i ti stvaraš mrežu.

882
00:39:01,400 --> 00:39:06,219
[SPEAKER_01] I sad dolazi vrijeme ratovanja mreža proti mreža.

883
00:39:06,219 --> 00:39:08,679
[SPEAKER_01] Rat mreža proti mreža.

884
00:39:08,679 --> 00:39:10,980
[SPEAKER_01] Tu mrežu možeš uništiti na dva načina.

885
00:39:10,980 --> 00:39:12,480
[SPEAKER_01] Da uništavaš ove čvorove,

886
00:39:13,260 --> 00:39:16,239
[SPEAKER_01] ili da prekineš vezu između tih čvorova.

887
00:39:16,239 --> 00:39:17,900
[SPEAKER_00] Odnosno, dotok komunikacije.

888
00:39:17,900 --> 00:39:18,360
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je.

889
00:39:18,360 --> 00:39:18,980
[SPEAKER_01] Informacije.

890
00:39:18,980 --> 00:39:23,079
[SPEAKER_01] E sad, ako je ovdje to radila umjetna inteligencija,

891
00:39:23,079 --> 00:39:25,280
[SPEAKER_01] onda sa i druge strane,

892
00:39:25,280 --> 00:39:27,699
[SPEAKER_01] tj. ruske, radila je umjetna inteligencija.

893
00:39:27,699 --> 00:39:30,360
[SPEAKER_01] Na način, ako se ovo o krakovi,

894
00:39:30,360 --> 00:39:33,360
[SPEAKER_01] sad ćemo mi krak jedan,

895
00:39:33,360 --> 00:39:36,659
[SPEAKER_01] odnosno isto dobri rezati jedan po drugi,

896
00:39:36,659 --> 00:39:37,539
[SPEAKER_01] zaustavljati ga.

897
00:39:37,539 --> 00:39:40,800
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, opet imaš s druge strane mrežu,

898
00:39:40,800 --> 00:39:42,300
[SPEAKER_01] opet sateliti ruski,

899
00:39:42,380 --> 00:39:43,820
[SPEAKER_01] sve umjetna inteligencija.

900
00:39:43,820 --> 00:39:44,860
[SPEAKER_01] I čega sad?

901
00:39:44,860 --> 00:39:46,099
[SPEAKER_01] Rusi stvaraju mrežu.

902
00:39:46,099 --> 00:39:48,820
[SPEAKER_01] Rusi nisu odmah u početku stvarali mrežu,

903
00:39:48,820 --> 00:39:49,820
[SPEAKER_01] jer nije bilo potrebno.

904
00:39:49,820 --> 00:39:53,119
[SPEAKER_01] Od ljudi, modula, hipermodula,

905
00:39:53,119 --> 00:39:54,420
[SPEAKER_01] oni će to kasnije uvesti.

906
00:39:54,420 --> 00:39:56,699
[SPEAKER_01] Sada za čišćenju proti napad,

907
00:39:56,699 --> 00:39:58,679
[SPEAKER_01] proti kontraofenzivi.

908
00:39:58,679 --> 00:40:00,719
[SPEAKER_01] Nego su to radili

909
00:40:00,719 --> 00:40:02,599
[SPEAKER_01] sa besplotnih letilicama,

910
00:40:02,599 --> 00:40:05,480
[SPEAKER_01] sa topništom i sa zrhoplostom.

911
00:40:05,480 --> 00:40:07,019
[SPEAKER_01] Udarali su te,

912
00:40:07,019 --> 00:40:08,840
[SPEAKER_01] pronalazili te skupine

913
00:40:08,840 --> 00:40:09,639
[SPEAKER_01] i udarali ih.

914
00:40:09,639 --> 00:40:11,500
[SPEAKER_01] I zato su veliki gubici

915
00:40:11,500 --> 00:40:14,019
[SPEAKER_01] strahotni su gubici tamo,

916
00:40:14,019 --> 00:40:15,099
[SPEAKER_01] što u svapadni mediji,

917
00:40:15,099 --> 00:40:16,260
[SPEAKER_01] mislim, ukrajinski, nažal,

918
00:40:16,260 --> 00:40:16,900
[SPEAKER_01] ima i ruski,

919
00:40:16,900 --> 00:40:17,880
[SPEAKER_01] da se odmah razumijemo.

920
00:40:17,880 --> 00:40:22,059
[SPEAKER_01] Neke podaci kaže,

921
00:40:22,059 --> 00:40:25,519
[SPEAKER_01] od 8 do 12 tisuća ljudi su izgubili.

922
00:40:25,519 --> 00:40:27,659
[SPEAKER_01] Izgubili su preko 100 tenkova.

923
00:40:27,659 --> 00:40:30,039
[SPEAKER_01] Izgubili su preko tisuću

924
00:40:30,039 --> 00:40:31,820
[SPEAKER_01] raznoraznih oklopnih vozila

925
00:40:31,820 --> 00:40:32,980
[SPEAKER_01] i vozila s nadbijevanja,

926
00:40:32,980 --> 00:40:34,119
[SPEAKER_01] logistike i tako dalje.

927
00:40:34,199 --> 00:40:35,320
[SPEAKER_01] To su strahotni gubici

928
00:40:35,320 --> 00:40:37,380
[SPEAKER_01] u jednom takvom kratnom vremenu

929
00:40:37,380 --> 00:40:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] za mjesec,

930
00:40:38,000 --> 00:40:38,980
[SPEAKER_01] na jednom takvom

931
00:40:38,980 --> 00:40:41,699
[SPEAKER_01] relativno nevelikom prostoru.

932
00:40:41,699 --> 00:40:42,840
[SPEAKER_00] To samo govori da

933
00:40:42,840 --> 00:40:44,579
[SPEAKER_00] ono, kako smo ratovanje,

934
00:40:44,579 --> 00:40:45,539
[SPEAKER_00] principe ratovanja,

935
00:40:45,539 --> 00:40:47,579
[SPEAKER_00] dosta znali da su otišli u povijest.

936
00:40:47,579 --> 00:40:48,280
[SPEAKER_01] Tako je.

937
00:40:48,280 --> 00:40:48,800
[SPEAKER_01] Gotovo je.

938
00:40:48,860 --> 00:40:49,239
[SPEAKER_01] Tako je.

939
00:40:49,239 --> 00:40:51,380
[SPEAKER_01] E, zašto ja to sve govorim?

940
00:40:51,380 --> 00:40:52,800
[SPEAKER_01] Ne govorim je uzavut.

941
00:40:52,800 --> 00:40:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] 18. godine je Hrvatska,

942
00:40:57,000 --> 00:40:57,900
[SPEAKER_01] dok je bio ministar,

943
00:40:57,900 --> 00:40:58,719
[SPEAKER_01] zato su ga i makli,

944
00:40:58,719 --> 00:41:00,539
[SPEAKER_01] išla u tom smjeru.

945
00:41:00,539 --> 00:41:02,780
[SPEAKER_01] Zato je ministar Krstićević

946
00:41:02,780 --> 00:41:04,420
[SPEAKER_01] sa svojim timom,

947
00:41:04,420 --> 00:41:05,199
[SPEAKER_01] onma donio odluku

948
00:41:05,199 --> 00:41:06,980
[SPEAKER_01] da se formira u udbini

