2759
01:37:40,260 --> 01:37:42,739
[SPEAKER_01] tehtonskih poremećaja

2760
01:37:42,739 --> 01:37:45,520
[SPEAKER_01] kakvih možda nisu bili

2761
01:37:45,520 --> 01:37:46,720
[SPEAKER_01] povijest ljudskog roda,

2762
01:37:46,720 --> 01:37:47,720
[SPEAKER_01] ali bilo ih je.

2763
01:37:47,720 --> 01:37:49,300
[SPEAKER_01] Ali možda ne nedavno.

2764
01:37:49,300 --> 01:37:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nemamo mojih,

2765
01:37:50,000 --> 01:37:50,739
[SPEAKER_01] mislim da je sad,

2766
01:37:50,739 --> 01:37:51,739
[SPEAKER_01] sad su ovo samo teško.

2767
01:37:51,739 --> 01:37:52,819
[SPEAKER_01] Ona je izuzetno teška,

2768
01:37:52,819 --> 01:37:53,659
[SPEAKER_01] ali ovdje su teška

2769
01:37:53,659 --> 01:37:55,119
[SPEAKER_01] iz jednog dodatno teškoga,

2770
01:37:55,119 --> 01:37:58,140
[SPEAKER_01] što je Sotona ima oružje

2771
01:37:58,140 --> 01:38:01,199
[SPEAKER_01] koje mi nemamo.

2772
01:38:01,199 --> 01:38:03,739
[SPEAKER_01] Oni imaju znanja,

2773
01:38:03,739 --> 01:38:06,140
[SPEAKER_01] jer su oni kroz obrazani sustav

2774
01:38:06,140 --> 01:38:08,020
[SPEAKER_01] uništili nama znanja,

2775
01:38:08,020 --> 01:38:08,619
[SPEAKER_01] jer me uđimo,

2776
01:38:08,619 --> 01:38:10,140
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam samo na primjeru

2777
01:38:10,140 --> 01:38:12,420
[SPEAKER_01] ove glagoljice i ploče,

2778
01:38:12,420 --> 01:38:12,939
[SPEAKER_01] rekao,

2779
01:38:12,939 --> 01:38:14,960
[SPEAKER_01] i Slavena,

2780
01:38:14,960 --> 01:38:16,600
[SPEAKER_01] kako su oni zokrenili,

2781
01:38:16,600 --> 01:38:18,180
[SPEAKER_01] ti živiš u potpuno neistini,

2782
01:38:18,180 --> 01:38:18,939
[SPEAKER_01] ne znanju.

2783
01:38:18,939 --> 01:38:20,020
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle,

2784
01:38:20,020 --> 01:38:20,960
[SPEAKER_01] oni imaju to,

2785
01:38:20,960 --> 01:38:23,060
[SPEAKER_01] oni imaju strašno oružje,

2786
01:38:23,060 --> 01:38:24,140
[SPEAKER_01] to je mediji,

2787
01:38:24,140 --> 01:38:25,579
[SPEAKER_01] gdje mogu,

2788
01:38:25,579 --> 01:38:26,359
[SPEAKER_01] tehnički,

2789
01:38:26,359 --> 01:38:27,720
[SPEAKER_01] tehnologijski razvili,

2790
01:38:27,720 --> 01:38:29,720
[SPEAKER_01] do sadašnje umjetne inteligencije.

2791
01:38:29,720 --> 01:38:31,159
[SPEAKER_01] Još o gledateljima moram reći,

2792
01:38:31,159 --> 01:38:32,739
[SPEAKER_01] nije to umjetna inteligencija,

2793
01:38:32,800 --> 01:38:34,600
[SPEAKER_01] inteligencija koju Bog daje u čovjeku.

2794
01:38:34,600 --> 01:38:36,520
[SPEAKER_01] To je jednostavno algoritam,

2795
01:38:36,520 --> 01:38:39,100
[SPEAKER_01] to nema veze sa inteligencijom,

2796
01:38:39,100 --> 01:38:40,399
[SPEAKER_01] nego je to algoritam

2797
01:38:40,399 --> 01:38:42,579
[SPEAKER_01] koji može sam sebi proizvoditi algoritme,

2798
01:38:42,579 --> 01:38:45,380
[SPEAKER_01] da bi brzo pretraživao nešto što već ima.

2799
01:38:45,380 --> 01:38:47,380
[SPEAKER_01] To je ništa i sintetizirao

2800
01:38:47,380 --> 01:38:49,520
[SPEAKER_01] po nekim svojim parametrema.

2801
01:38:49,520 --> 01:38:50,899
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, radi se o algoritmu,

2802
01:38:50,899 --> 01:38:51,979
[SPEAKER_01] ali eto,

2803
01:38:51,979 --> 01:38:54,039
[SPEAKER_01] vrlo prijemčiva je umjetna inteligencija.

2804
01:38:54,039 --> 01:38:55,220
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle,

2805
01:38:55,220 --> 01:38:57,079
[SPEAKER_01] ta su vremena sada teška.

2806
01:38:57,079 --> 01:38:58,579
[SPEAKER_01] Ono što se,

2807
01:38:58,579 --> 01:39:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] svaka strategija,

2808
01:39:00,000 --> 01:39:02,579
[SPEAKER_01] ima protu strategiju.

2809
01:39:03,180 --> 01:39:04,840
[SPEAKER_01] Ako mi u domovinskom ratu

2810
01:39:04,840 --> 01:39:06,619
[SPEAKER_01] nismo imali oružja,

2811
01:39:06,619 --> 01:39:07,600
[SPEAKER_01] koje ima oružje?

2812
01:39:07,600 --> 01:39:08,479
[SPEAKER_01] I na.

2813
01:39:08,479 --> 01:39:11,380
[SPEAKER_01] Ja znam kada smo bili taj sasranak

2814
01:39:11,380 --> 01:39:12,020
[SPEAKER_01] sa predsjednikom tuđima.

2815
01:39:12,020 --> 01:39:13,380
[SPEAKER_01] Pa šta učiniti ono sve pat?

2816
01:39:13,380 --> 01:39:14,579
[SPEAKER_01] Pa predsjedniće,

2817
01:39:14,579 --> 01:39:15,239
[SPEAKER_01] koje ima oružje?

2818
01:39:15,239 --> 01:39:17,260
[SPEAKER_01] Pa kako koje ima?

2819
01:39:17,260 --> 01:39:17,979
[SPEAKER_01] Pa i na.

2820
01:39:17,979 --> 01:39:19,680
[SPEAKER_01] Pa uzvećemo od njih.

2821
01:39:19,680 --> 01:39:21,260
[SPEAKER_01] E, tako i ovdje.

2822
01:39:21,260 --> 01:39:23,180
[SPEAKER_01] Sada i ovi mediji

2823
01:39:23,180 --> 01:39:25,659
[SPEAKER_01] uzmemo oružje od njih.

2824
01:39:25,659 --> 01:39:28,199
[SPEAKER_01] Ako se oni napravili rat mreža,

2825
01:39:28,199 --> 01:39:30,060
[SPEAKER_01] napravimo i mi čvorove

2826
01:39:30,060 --> 01:39:31,380
[SPEAKER_01] na tim mrežama,

2827
01:39:31,380 --> 01:39:32,659
[SPEAKER_01] a to znači ovakve,

2828
01:39:32,720 --> 01:39:33,800
[SPEAKER_01] alternativni mediji,

2829
01:39:33,800 --> 01:39:35,100
[SPEAKER_01] u kojim će se govoriti

2830
01:39:35,100 --> 01:39:35,600
[SPEAKER_01] istina.

2831
01:39:35,600 --> 01:39:39,100
[SPEAKER_01] Ima puno ljudi u Hrvatskoj,

2832
01:39:39,100 --> 01:39:40,399
[SPEAKER_01] u svim područjima,

2833
01:39:40,399 --> 01:39:42,060
[SPEAKER_01] koje znaju govoriti

2834
01:39:42,060 --> 01:39:43,720
[SPEAKER_01] na istinski način.

2835
01:39:43,720 --> 01:39:44,779
[SPEAKER_01] Ja govorim sa stališta

2836
01:39:44,779 --> 01:39:46,100
[SPEAKER_01] geostrategije i geopolitike

2837
01:39:46,100 --> 01:39:46,880
[SPEAKER_01] i vojnog omijeća,

2838
01:39:46,880 --> 01:39:48,479
[SPEAKER_01] ali ima i znastanika,

2839
01:39:48,479 --> 01:39:49,800
[SPEAKER_01] ima i svih kulturnih djelatnik,

2840
01:39:49,800 --> 01:39:50,720
[SPEAKER_01] ima svih mogućih

2841
01:39:50,720 --> 01:39:51,960
[SPEAKER_01] koji mogu govoriti.

2842
01:39:51,960 --> 01:39:52,859
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, ima,

2843
01:39:52,859 --> 01:39:53,859
[SPEAKER_01] ali ovi si od nas.

2844
01:39:53,859 --> 01:39:55,640
[SPEAKER_01] E, više nema mlakih duša.

2845
01:39:56,100 --> 01:39:57,579
[SPEAKER_01] Kristi je rekao da smo

2846
01:39:57,579 --> 01:40:00,279
[SPEAKER_01] najgore mlake duše.

2847
01:40:00,279 --> 01:40:01,100
[SPEAKER_01] E, prema tome,

2848
01:40:01,100 --> 01:40:03,060
[SPEAKER_01] uzimimo od Kristovog nauka

2849
01:40:03,060 --> 01:40:04,840
[SPEAKER_01] i ne budimo više mlake duše,

2850
01:40:04,840 --> 01:40:05,960
[SPEAKER_01] nego krenemo se,

2851
01:40:05,960 --> 01:40:06,840
[SPEAKER_01] uprostavimo se,

2852
01:40:06,840 --> 01:40:07,840
[SPEAKER_01] govorimo.

2853
01:40:08,319 --> 01:40:09,500
[SPEAKER_01] Ovo je misija govorenja

2854
01:40:09,500 --> 01:40:10,859
[SPEAKER_01] koliko mogu sad razubjeti.

2855
01:40:10,859 --> 01:40:12,340
[SPEAKER_01] Zato sam i rado pristao

2856
01:40:12,340 --> 01:40:13,479
[SPEAKER_01] i došao i tako dalje,

2857
01:40:13,479 --> 01:40:14,760
[SPEAKER_01] jer je vrijeme sad govoriti.

2858
01:40:14,760 --> 01:40:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] I govorit ćemo i dalje.

2859
01:40:16,000 --> 01:40:17,279
[SPEAKER_00] Da, kad, ako ne sad.

2860
01:40:17,279 --> 01:40:18,119
[SPEAKER_00] Ako ne sad.

2861
01:40:18,119 --> 01:40:19,979
[SPEAKER_01] Dobro, pa velika je sreća,

2862
01:40:19,979 --> 01:40:21,939
[SPEAKER_00] znate, kad imamo te medije

2863
01:40:21,939 --> 01:40:23,560
[SPEAKER_00] koji misle umjesto nas.

2864
01:40:23,560 --> 01:40:27,260
[SPEAKER_01] Da, pa ne, ne, ne, ne, ne.

2865
01:40:27,260 --> 01:40:28,159
[SPEAKER_01] Ne moramo se mučiti

2866
01:40:28,159 --> 01:40:28,260
[SPEAKER_01] s razmišljenjem.

2867
01:40:28,260 --> 01:40:29,699
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, ne, čak i ovo,

2868
01:40:29,699 --> 01:40:30,520
[SPEAKER_01] mislijem već su nas.

2869
01:40:30,520 --> 01:40:32,939
[SPEAKER_01] Oni čak ne misliju oni

2870
01:40:32,939 --> 01:40:33,479
[SPEAKER_01] misliju nas,

2871
01:40:33,479 --> 01:40:35,220
[SPEAKER_01] nego oni nama ne daju misliti.

2872
01:40:35,220 --> 01:40:35,659
[SPEAKER_01] Eda.

2873
01:40:36,000 --> 01:40:37,359
[SPEAKER_01] Oni nama jednostavno ne daju.

2874
01:40:37,359 --> 01:40:37,960
[SPEAKER_00] Da, da, zapravo sve čine

2875
01:40:37,960 --> 01:40:39,220
[SPEAKER_00] da nama bude ljepše.

2876
01:40:39,220 --> 01:40:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da, ja moram se malo šalim.

2877
01:40:41,000 --> 01:40:41,020
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da, ja moram se malo šalim.

2878
01:40:41,020 --> 01:40:44,960
[SPEAKER_00] Admirale, htjela sam vas

2879
01:40:44,960 --> 01:40:45,760
[SPEAKER_00] još nešto pitati.

2880
01:40:45,760 --> 01:40:46,779
[SPEAKER_00] Malo prije smo spomenuli

2881
01:40:46,779 --> 01:40:48,659
[SPEAKER_00] BRICS i mogućnost.

2882
01:40:48,659 --> 01:40:50,640
[SPEAKER_00] Putin je pozvao tamo

2883
01:40:50,640 --> 01:40:51,619
[SPEAKER_00] Aleksandra Vučića,

2884
01:40:51,619 --> 01:40:52,420
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno Srbiju.

2885
01:40:52,420 --> 01:40:53,819
[SPEAKER_00] Nas niko nikud ne zove.

2886
01:40:53,819 --> 01:40:55,840
[SPEAKER_00] U Srbiju stalno neko nešto ide.

2887
01:40:55,840 --> 01:40:57,640
[SPEAKER_00] Makoliko se mi kao rugali

2888
01:40:57,640 --> 01:40:58,739
[SPEAKER_00] tim Srbima.

2889
01:40:58,739 --> 01:41:00,439
[SPEAKER_00] Ispada da je najprije Vučić

2890
01:41:00,439 --> 01:41:01,899
[SPEAKER_00] rekao Putinu njet,

2891
01:41:02,260 --> 01:41:03,880
[SPEAKER_00] neće tamo u BRICS.

2892
01:41:03,880 --> 01:41:05,060
[SPEAKER_00] A onda sad malo nešto.

2893
01:41:05,060 --> 01:41:06,760
[SPEAKER_00] A jo, imam gužu užas na Istercu.

2894
01:41:06,760 --> 01:41:07,659
[SPEAKER_00] Što vi mislite?

2895
01:41:07,659 --> 01:41:09,159
[SPEAKER_00] Što će biti sa tom Srbijom i BRICS-om?

2896
01:41:09,159 --> 01:41:10,439
[SPEAKER_01] Ova, gdje smo lijepo rekli

2897
01:41:10,439 --> 01:41:11,560
[SPEAKER_01] jednom iz svi trenutka

2898
01:41:11,560 --> 01:41:13,239
[SPEAKER_01] da Plejković i Vučić služi

2899
01:41:13,239 --> 01:41:14,260
[SPEAKER_01] iz toga šefu.

2900
01:41:14,260 --> 01:41:14,579
[SPEAKER_01] Evo ga.

2901
01:41:14,579 --> 01:41:15,760
[SPEAKER_01] Ko što je služio,

2902
01:41:15,760 --> 01:41:17,180
[SPEAKER_01] da gledam kao što je

2903
01:41:17,180 --> 01:41:19,720
[SPEAKER_01] Pavelić i ti to slušili

2904
01:41:19,720 --> 01:41:20,819
[SPEAKER_01] iz toga šefa.

2905
01:41:20,819 --> 01:41:21,859
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, tako da smo...

2906
01:41:21,859 --> 01:41:22,979
[SPEAKER_01] Ne da u Bog to reči.

2907
01:41:22,979 --> 01:41:25,319
[SPEAKER_01] Ovaj šef bio u Londonu

2908
01:41:25,319 --> 01:41:26,640
[SPEAKER_01] tada u to vrijeme,

2909
01:41:26,640 --> 01:41:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] a ovaj šef je u Briselu.

2910
01:41:28,000 --> 01:41:29,880
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, da se odmah razume.

2911
01:41:29,880 --> 01:41:31,260
[SPEAKER_01] Srbi ko Srbi.

2912
01:41:31,260 --> 01:41:32,600
[SPEAKER_01] Vučić ko Vučić.

2913
01:41:32,600 --> 01:41:33,739
[SPEAKER_01] On je,

2914
01:41:33,739 --> 01:41:35,720
[SPEAKER_01] to je jedna tragična figura.

2915
01:41:35,720 --> 01:41:36,720
[SPEAKER_01] Ja ne znaš nešto,

2916
01:41:36,779 --> 01:41:37,699
[SPEAKER_01] mi uopće njemu davamo

2917
01:41:37,699 --> 01:41:38,840
[SPEAKER_01] neko posebno značenje.

2918
01:41:38,840 --> 01:41:39,779
[SPEAKER_01] Ja stoji sa Srba,

2919
01:41:39,779 --> 01:41:41,279
[SPEAKER_01] rekao ovako u razgovorima

2920
01:41:41,279 --> 01:41:41,600
[SPEAKER_01] i ostalo.

2921
01:41:41,600 --> 01:41:44,739
[SPEAKER_01] Pa da, što mu uopće dajde?

2922
01:41:44,739 --> 01:41:46,140
[SPEAKER_01] Pa on je pristao.

2923
01:41:46,140 --> 01:41:48,100
[SPEAKER_01] Samo ne smije obznaniti

2924
01:41:48,100 --> 01:41:50,899
[SPEAKER_01] da samostalnost Kosova.

2925
01:41:50,899 --> 01:41:52,539
[SPEAKER_01] A samostalnost Kosova znači

2926
01:41:52,539 --> 01:41:53,720
[SPEAKER_01] stvaranje Velike Albanije.

2927
01:41:53,720 --> 01:41:55,340
[SPEAKER_01] Jer je to plan ameriški.

2928
01:41:55,340 --> 01:41:56,899
[SPEAKER_01] I sad on lavitira.

2929
01:41:56,899 --> 01:41:58,859
[SPEAKER_01] Ima kako Srbija,

2930
01:41:58,859 --> 01:41:59,880
[SPEAKER_01] to je izišlo vani,

2931
01:41:59,880 --> 01:42:00,899
[SPEAKER_01] daje oružje Ukrajinu,

2932
01:42:00,899 --> 01:42:03,140
[SPEAKER_01] ko što smo i mi davali.

2933
01:42:03,140 --> 01:42:04,239
[SPEAKER_01] Znači kakva je razlika

2934
01:42:04,239 --> 01:42:05,539
[SPEAKER_01] između politike Srbije

2935
01:42:05,539 --> 01:42:06,479
[SPEAKER_01] i politike Hrvatske.

2936
01:42:06,479 --> 01:42:06,859
[SPEAKER_01] Nema.

2937
01:42:06,859 --> 01:42:09,060
[SPEAKER_01] I mi i oni daju oružje.

2938
01:42:09,060 --> 01:42:10,560
[SPEAKER_01] Odnosno, mi još dajemo nos.

2939
01:42:10,560 --> 01:42:11,960
[SPEAKER_01] On vjerojatno nije dao

2940
01:42:11,960 --> 01:42:12,819
[SPEAKER_01] 200 milijuna.

2941
01:42:12,819 --> 01:42:15,020
[SPEAKER_01] A eto, naš Plenković je dao

2942
01:42:15,020 --> 01:42:15,500
[SPEAKER_01] 200 milijuna.

2943
01:42:15,500 --> 01:42:16,819
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro, mi smo bogati.

2944
01:42:16,819 --> 01:42:18,859
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, ne, ne, mi smo u šire duše.

2945
01:42:18,859 --> 01:42:19,779
[SPEAKER_01] Mi smo, evo, tako je.

2946
01:42:19,779 --> 01:42:20,779
[SPEAKER_01] I ostalo ga.

2947
01:42:20,779 --> 01:42:24,659
[SPEAKER_01] I onda on, vjerojatno prvo je rekao da neće,

2948
01:42:24,659 --> 01:42:26,600
[SPEAKER_01] jer mu je to trebalo iz Brisila.

2949
01:42:26,600 --> 01:42:28,960
[SPEAKER_01] Onda su ovi vjerojatno mu rekli,

2950
01:42:28,960 --> 01:42:30,500
[SPEAKER_01] u Srbiji, Rima tamo.

2951
01:42:30,500 --> 01:42:32,760
[SPEAKER_01] Mi su oni rekli mu, slušaj,

2952
01:42:32,760 --> 01:42:33,760
[SPEAKER_01] jer su već im to rekli,

2953
01:42:33,760 --> 01:42:34,399
[SPEAKER_01] ovo što ću reći.

2954
01:42:34,399 --> 01:42:35,659
[SPEAKER_01] Vučiću, znaš,

2955
01:42:35,659 --> 01:42:36,800
[SPEAKER_01] ako ti to uradiš,

2956
01:42:36,800 --> 01:42:38,819
[SPEAKER_01] odnosno, za Kosovu,

2957
01:42:38,819 --> 01:42:40,060
[SPEAKER_01] a u ovom slučaju smo rekli,

2958
01:42:40,060 --> 01:42:40,800
[SPEAKER_01] slušaj Vučiću,

2959
01:42:41,119 --> 01:42:42,020
[SPEAKER_01] Ako ti ne ideš tamo,

2960
01:42:42,020 --> 01:42:43,319
[SPEAKER_01] sveće ćete dogoreti.

2961
01:42:43,319 --> 01:42:46,520
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, kod njih nema igre.

2962
01:42:46,520 --> 01:42:52,020
[SPEAKER_01] I onda je on sklon takvim perturbacijama,

2963
01:42:52,020 --> 01:42:54,340
[SPEAKER_01] jer je vezan.

2964
01:42:54,340 --> 01:42:56,500
[SPEAKER_01] On je prodao dušu džavolu.

2965
01:42:56,500 --> 01:42:58,180
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, jednostavno rečeno.

2966
01:42:58,180 --> 01:43:00,220
[SPEAKER_01] I onda on samo hoće spasti,

2967
01:43:00,220 --> 01:43:02,720
[SPEAKER_01] ali duši jer je nema,

2968
01:43:02,720 --> 01:43:04,819
[SPEAKER_01] jer im je džavol rada njegovom dušom,

2969
01:43:04,819 --> 01:43:06,619
[SPEAKER_01] svakom ko prodao dušu džavolu,

2970
01:43:06,619 --> 01:43:09,119
[SPEAKER_01] da ne govorim i kod nas to,

2971
01:43:09,119 --> 01:43:10,500
[SPEAKER_01] neću, ajde, sad naše,

2972
01:43:10,500 --> 01:43:11,819
[SPEAKER_01] ne smijem toliko kao admiral

2973
01:43:11,819 --> 01:43:12,939
[SPEAKER_01] i bivši način glavništva,

2974
01:43:12,939 --> 01:43:14,100
[SPEAKER_01] želim na takav način govoriti.

2975
01:43:14,100 --> 01:43:16,279
[SPEAKER_01] I to je njegova sada politika.

2976
01:43:16,279 --> 01:43:17,880
[SPEAKER_01] To je, dakle, politika bez politike,

2977
01:43:17,880 --> 01:43:18,380
[SPEAKER_01] jednostavno.

2978
01:43:18,380 --> 01:43:18,859
[SPEAKER_01] Sve jasno.

2979
01:43:18,859 --> 01:43:20,659
[SPEAKER_00] Ali svejedno, evo, za kraj,

2980
01:43:20,659 --> 01:43:23,640
[SPEAKER_00] Šefcije je nedavno naglo bio u Sarajevu,

2981
01:43:23,640 --> 01:43:24,619
[SPEAKER_00] pa je otišao u Belgrad,

2982
01:43:24,619 --> 01:43:25,699
[SPEAKER_00] Zagreba vidio nije,

2983
01:43:25,699 --> 01:43:27,079
[SPEAKER_00] a mi smo kao neki partneri.

2984
01:43:27,079 --> 01:43:30,279
[SPEAKER_01] Pa on hoće, šta će on partnere?

2985
01:43:30,279 --> 01:43:31,520
[SPEAKER_01] Nikakvi mi nismo partnere,

2986
01:43:31,520 --> 01:43:32,420
[SPEAKER_01] mi smo poslušnice,

2987
01:43:32,420 --> 01:43:33,539
[SPEAKER_01] šta će on raditi kod nas?

2988
01:43:33,960 --> 01:43:35,600
[SPEAKER_01] Jer mi slušamo što kažu.

2989
01:43:35,600 --> 01:43:37,060
[SPEAKER_00] A što je onda išao u Bosnu?

2990
01:43:37,060 --> 01:43:39,159
[SPEAKER_01] Pa išao u Jugoslaviju obavljati.

2991
01:43:39,159 --> 01:43:41,460
[SPEAKER_01] Pa to je ovo što mu govorimo u Jugoslaviju.

2992
01:43:41,460 --> 01:43:42,539
[SPEAKER_01] Jer to je sve isto vrijeme

2993
01:43:42,539 --> 01:43:45,800
[SPEAKER_01] kad ovi imaju kulturne izričaje,

2994
01:43:45,800 --> 01:43:47,760
[SPEAKER_01] šustrat na tromeđi.

2995
01:43:47,760 --> 01:43:49,319
[SPEAKER_01] E kada se,

2996
01:43:49,319 --> 01:43:50,680
[SPEAKER_01] ovaj,

2997
01:43:50,680 --> 01:43:52,079
[SPEAKER_01] bijelo dugme

2998
01:43:52,079 --> 01:43:54,420
[SPEAKER_01] Jugoslavijsku zastavu izvijezdu.

2999
01:43:54,420 --> 01:43:55,939
[SPEAKER_01] Pa to su te iste priče.

3000
01:43:56,479 --> 01:43:58,039
[SPEAKER_01] E vidiš,

3001
01:43:58,039 --> 01:43:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] to je strategija

3002
01:43:59,000 --> 01:44:01,180
[SPEAKER_01] kada ti posložiš

3003
01:44:01,180 --> 01:44:02,500
[SPEAKER_01] u istu priču,

3004
01:44:02,500 --> 01:44:04,079
[SPEAKER_01] to je strategija,

3005
01:44:04,079 --> 01:44:04,680
[SPEAKER_01] obuhvatno,

3006
01:44:04,680 --> 01:44:05,819
[SPEAKER_01] jer je s obuhvatno,

3007
01:44:05,819 --> 01:44:08,079
[SPEAKER_01] događaje koje su razbacali

3008
01:44:08,079 --> 01:44:10,119
[SPEAKER_01] ili događaje koje su pomaknuti

3009
01:44:10,119 --> 01:44:10,960
[SPEAKER_01] u vremenima,

3010
01:44:10,960 --> 01:44:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] pa i tišću godina.

3011
01:44:13,000 --> 01:44:14,579
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, to dio iste priče.

3012
01:44:14,579 --> 01:44:17,340
[SPEAKER_01] Jer je najbolje njima bilo spriječiti,

3013
01:44:17,340 --> 01:44:19,199
[SPEAKER_01] jer sada nakon

3014
01:44:19,199 --> 01:44:21,800
[SPEAKER_01] ruske pobjede u Ukrajini,

3015
01:44:21,800 --> 01:44:23,739
[SPEAKER_01] sad je Rusija ide projekciju

3016
01:44:23,739 --> 01:44:24,340
[SPEAKER_01] svoje moći

3017
01:44:24,340 --> 01:44:26,680
[SPEAKER_01] na sredinu sredozemlje.

3018
01:44:26,680 --> 01:44:27,460
[SPEAKER_01] A što mislite?

3019
01:44:27,460 --> 01:44:28,039
[SPEAKER_01] Gdje će srati put?

3020
01:44:28,039 --> 01:44:30,199
[SPEAKER_01] Sredinu sredna progresija moći.

3021
01:44:30,199 --> 01:44:31,500
[SPEAKER_01] Ne samo vojne,

3022
01:44:31,500 --> 01:44:32,880
[SPEAKER_01] nego sve druge moći,

3023
01:44:32,880 --> 01:44:33,560
[SPEAKER_01] geopolitičke,

3024
01:44:33,560 --> 01:44:34,239
[SPEAKER_01] onda sve redo,

3025
01:44:34,239 --> 01:44:36,479
[SPEAKER_01] energesku da ne govorim.

3026
01:44:36,479 --> 01:44:38,899
[SPEAKER_01] Ko je spriječavao to isto

3027
01:44:38,899 --> 01:44:39,899
[SPEAKER_01] u vrijeme hladnog rata?

3028
01:44:39,899 --> 01:44:40,739
[SPEAKER_01] Jugoslavija.

3029
01:44:40,739 --> 01:44:42,159
[SPEAKER_01] Zato je Jugoslavija stvorena.

3030
01:44:42,159 --> 01:44:44,060
[SPEAKER_01] Zato je stvoren pokret nesrstani.

3031
01:44:44,060 --> 01:44:45,680
[SPEAKER_01] Nije pokret nesrstani

3032
01:44:45,680 --> 01:44:46,619
[SPEAKER_01] izmišljotna Tita,

3033
01:44:46,619 --> 01:44:47,760
[SPEAKER_01] što vi govorio,

3034
01:44:47,760 --> 01:44:49,479
[SPEAKER_01] nego izmišljotna aglosaksonaca,

3035
01:44:49,899 --> 01:44:52,520
[SPEAKER_01] jer je pomoću pokrata nesrstani

3036
01:44:52,520 --> 01:44:53,659
[SPEAKER_01] Tito dobio zadaću

3037
01:44:53,659 --> 01:44:55,199
[SPEAKER_01] da diljem svijeta okupi

3038
01:44:55,199 --> 01:44:57,239
[SPEAKER_01] da ne bi provadilo utjecaj Kine

3039
01:44:57,239 --> 01:44:58,739
[SPEAKER_01] i Sovjetskog saveza ondašnjeg.

3040
01:44:58,739 --> 01:45:02,060
[SPEAKER_01] Sad je ista geopolitička priča

3041
01:45:02,060 --> 01:45:03,239
[SPEAKER_01] samo pomaknuta ova vremena.

3042
01:45:03,239 --> 01:45:04,159
[SPEAKER_01] Ista.

3043
01:45:04,159 --> 01:45:05,319
[SPEAKER_00] Admirale, gdje će Putin stati?

3044
01:45:05,319 --> 01:45:06,880
[SPEAKER_01] Zato njima je ognava Jugoslavije.

3045
01:45:06,880 --> 01:45:08,539
[SPEAKER_00] Gdje će Putin stati?

3046
01:45:08,539 --> 01:45:10,500
[SPEAKER_01] Kako neće on stati ništa,

3047
01:45:10,500 --> 01:45:11,619
[SPEAKER_01] on će uznaći što je.

3048
01:45:11,619 --> 01:45:12,720
[SPEAKER_01] Ono što je bio

3049
01:45:12,720 --> 01:45:13,600
[SPEAKER_01] Varsavski ugovor,

3050
01:45:13,600 --> 01:45:14,380
[SPEAKER_01] to je...

3051
01:45:14,380 --> 01:45:16,039
[SPEAKER_01] Opet, sad ćemo opet krivo

3052
01:45:16,039 --> 01:45:17,100
[SPEAKER_01] stvati da navinja za Rusa.

3053
01:45:17,100 --> 01:45:17,640
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, ne, ne.

3054
01:45:17,640 --> 01:45:19,739
[SPEAKER_00] Samo neka ljudi razmišljaju.

3055
01:45:19,739 --> 01:45:20,640
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, ne, ovako.

3056
01:45:20,640 --> 01:45:23,899
[SPEAKER_01] Do sada je bio jednopolarni svijet.

3057
01:45:23,899 --> 01:45:25,659
[SPEAKER_01] Aglosaksonski, vlast,

3058
01:45:25,659 --> 01:45:26,460
[SPEAKER_01] sto godina,

3059
01:45:26,460 --> 01:45:29,520
[SPEAKER_01] čak je Bush prvi

3060
01:45:29,520 --> 01:45:30,840
[SPEAKER_01] nakon pustinske uluje

3061
01:45:30,840 --> 01:45:32,319
[SPEAKER_01] rekao da će biti

3062
01:45:32,319 --> 01:45:33,340
[SPEAKER_01] 21. stoljeće,

3063
01:45:33,399 --> 01:45:34,479
[SPEAKER_01] biti američko stoljeće.

3064
01:45:34,479 --> 01:45:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, oni su apsolutni gospodari.

3065
01:45:36,000 --> 01:45:37,500
[SPEAKER_01] I oni su se tako ponašali.

3066
01:45:37,500 --> 01:45:39,619
[SPEAKER_01] Ako si ti gospodar,

3067
01:45:39,619 --> 01:45:40,819
[SPEAKER_01] znači svaku pojavu

3068
01:45:40,819 --> 01:45:41,760
[SPEAKER_01] nekoga drugoga

3069
01:45:41,760 --> 01:45:42,859
[SPEAKER_01] koji ti može osporiti

3070
01:45:42,859 --> 01:45:43,319
[SPEAKER_01] tvoju moć,

3071
01:45:43,319 --> 01:45:44,159
[SPEAKER_01] moraš ga uništiti.

3072
01:45:44,159 --> 01:45:45,420
[SPEAKER_01] E sad,

3073
01:45:45,420 --> 01:45:47,539
[SPEAKER_01] oni nisu predvidjeli

3074
01:45:47,539 --> 01:45:48,939
[SPEAKER_01] ili bi onaj pijani jelicin,

3075
01:45:48,939 --> 01:45:50,239
[SPEAKER_01] Rusija bila u koljenima,

3076
01:45:50,239 --> 01:45:51,720
[SPEAKER_01] nisu predvidjeli

3077
01:45:51,720 --> 01:45:53,039
[SPEAKER_01] asimetršnog ratnika

3078
01:45:53,039 --> 01:45:53,640
[SPEAKER_01] koji se zove

3079
01:45:53,640 --> 01:45:54,920
[SPEAKER_01] Vladimir Imanirović Putin

3080
01:45:54,920 --> 01:45:55,539
[SPEAKER_01] iz pepela,

3081
01:45:55,539 --> 01:45:56,220
[SPEAKER_01] kao Feniks,

3082
01:45:56,220 --> 01:45:57,960
[SPEAKER_01] digao je Rusiju.

3083
01:45:57,960 --> 01:45:59,500
[SPEAKER_01] Na vrh,

3084
01:45:59,500 --> 01:46:01,119
[SPEAKER_01] vojno je doveo

3085
01:46:01,119 --> 01:46:02,699
[SPEAKER_01] sa velikom projekcijom moći,

3086
01:46:02,699 --> 01:46:03,840
[SPEAKER_01] sa kriperzvučnih oružima

3087
01:46:03,840 --> 01:46:04,779
[SPEAKER_01] koje zapad još nema.

3088
01:46:04,779 --> 01:46:05,659
[SPEAKER_01] I nema odgovoru na to.

3089
01:46:05,659 --> 01:46:06,939
[SPEAKER_01] S druge strane,

3090
01:46:06,939 --> 01:46:08,779
[SPEAKER_01] Kina je ona,

3091
01:46:08,779 --> 01:46:09,939
[SPEAKER_01] a ko je otvorio Kini?

3092
01:46:09,939 --> 01:46:12,100
[SPEAKER_01] Pa otvorio Kini Amerikar

3093
01:46:12,100 --> 01:46:12,680
[SPEAKER_01] su mislili da će

3094
01:46:12,680 --> 01:46:14,100
[SPEAKER_01] pomoću jeftine ratne snage

3095
01:46:14,100 --> 01:46:15,840
[SPEAKER_01] imati ekstratne profite

3096
01:46:15,840 --> 01:46:20,260
[SPEAKER_01] u vrijeme Kissingera,

3097
01:46:20,260 --> 01:46:22,300
[SPEAKER_01] 70. godina prošloga stoljeća.

3098
01:46:22,300 --> 01:46:23,380
[SPEAKER_01] Kina napravila

3099
01:46:23,380 --> 01:46:24,300
[SPEAKER_01] paralni sustav

3100
01:46:24,300 --> 01:46:26,300
[SPEAKER_01] i digla svoje gospodarstvo.

3101
01:46:26,300 --> 01:46:26,760
[SPEAKER_01] I pojela ih.

3102
01:46:26,760 --> 01:46:27,720
[SPEAKER_01] I pojela ih.

3103
01:46:27,720 --> 01:46:29,560
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, imaš vojnu silu projekcije,

3104
01:46:29,560 --> 01:46:30,439
[SPEAKER_01] imaš gospodarsko.

3105
01:46:30,439 --> 01:46:31,460
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, što hoću reći?

3106
01:46:31,460 --> 01:46:32,659
[SPEAKER_01] Hoću reći da je sada

3107
01:46:32,659 --> 01:46:34,800
[SPEAKER_01] više polarnost svijeta,

3108
01:46:34,800 --> 01:46:35,779
[SPEAKER_01] da ne ima Amerika.

3109
01:46:35,779 --> 01:46:36,779
[SPEAKER_01] A oni se toga

3110
01:46:36,779 --> 01:46:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] ne žele odreći.

3111
01:46:38,000 --> 01:46:38,699
[SPEAKER_01] Ne Amerika,

3112
01:46:38,699 --> 01:46:39,600
[SPEAKER_01] kao Amerika,

3113
01:46:39,600 --> 01:46:40,279
[SPEAKER_01] kao država.

3114
01:46:40,279 --> 01:46:41,779
[SPEAKER_01] To ga je Trump svjeso,

3115
01:46:41,779 --> 01:46:42,680
[SPEAKER_01] zato njima smeta.

3116
01:46:43,180 --> 01:46:44,439
[SPEAKER_01] nego je Amerika bila,

3117
01:46:44,439 --> 01:46:45,779
[SPEAKER_01] što uvijek gonavni ponavljaću,

3118
01:46:45,779 --> 01:46:47,479
[SPEAKER_01] velika batina u rukama

3119
01:46:47,479 --> 01:46:48,460
[SPEAKER_01] okultne oligarkije

3120
01:46:48,460 --> 01:46:49,979
[SPEAKER_01] da ona mogla tu ući

3121
01:46:49,979 --> 01:46:51,380
[SPEAKER_01] gdje dijela po svijetu

3122
01:46:51,380 --> 01:46:52,380
[SPEAKER_01] i uzimati

3123
01:46:52,380 --> 01:46:54,520
[SPEAKER_01] izvaronosne resurse.

3124
01:46:54,520 --> 01:46:54,840
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle,

3125
01:46:54,840 --> 01:46:57,500
[SPEAKER_01] sad ima više polarnost svijeta.

3126
01:46:57,500 --> 01:46:59,619
[SPEAKER_01] Ako ima ta tri velika tabora,

3127
01:46:59,619 --> 01:47:00,720
[SPEAKER_01] to je prva razina.

3128
01:47:00,720 --> 01:47:01,340
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle,

3129
01:47:01,340 --> 01:47:02,380
[SPEAKER_01] Svije njamečke države,

3130
01:47:02,380 --> 01:47:03,279
[SPEAKER_01] oni će i dalje biti,

3131
01:47:03,279 --> 01:47:04,779
[SPEAKER_01] velosilnika koje tu dvojbe nema,

3132
01:47:04,779 --> 01:47:06,619
[SPEAKER_01] biće Rusija i biće Kina.

3133
01:47:06,619 --> 01:47:08,500
[SPEAKER_01] One su tri glavna igrača.

3134
01:47:08,500 --> 01:47:09,539
[SPEAKER_01] I odnos između njih.

3135
01:47:09,539 --> 01:47:10,239
[SPEAKER_01] Ja to pišem,

3136
01:47:10,680 --> 01:47:12,399
[SPEAKER_01] između ostalo i u svojom novom knjizi

3137
01:47:12,399 --> 01:47:14,039
[SPEAKER_01] piše na kraju nešto o tome.

3138
01:47:14,039 --> 01:47:15,899
[SPEAKER_01] Ali sad u ovim knjigama

3139
01:47:15,899 --> 01:47:18,239
[SPEAKER_01] sad to do kraja razradio.

3140
01:47:18,239 --> 01:47:20,760
[SPEAKER_01] Ima druga razina,

3141
01:47:20,760 --> 01:47:22,039
[SPEAKER_01] to je Indija,

3142
01:47:22,039 --> 01:47:23,819
[SPEAKER_01] to je islamski svijet,

3143
01:47:23,819 --> 01:47:25,819
[SPEAKER_01] odnosno točnije,

3144
01:47:25,819 --> 01:47:27,300
[SPEAKER_01] islamski svijet bolje šire,

3145
01:47:27,300 --> 01:47:28,319
[SPEAKER_01] to je afrički svijet

3146
01:47:28,319 --> 01:47:29,800
[SPEAKER_01] i latinsko-američki svijet.

3147
01:47:29,800 --> 01:47:30,960
[SPEAKER_01] Svi su oni budu.

3148
01:47:30,960 --> 01:47:31,899
[SPEAKER_01] Evo vidimo,

3149
01:47:31,899 --> 01:47:32,779
[SPEAKER_01] sada je Kina,

3150
01:47:32,779 --> 01:47:34,720
[SPEAKER_01] u neki gospodarski forum,

3151
01:47:34,720 --> 01:47:37,939
[SPEAKER_01] 50 afričkih zemalja došlo je u Kinu

3152
01:47:37,939 --> 01:47:39,380
[SPEAKER_01] i ovaj sad kaže milijardu

3153
01:47:39,380 --> 01:47:40,960
[SPEAKER_01] joj ne zna šta će dati i ovi ostalo.

3154
01:47:40,960 --> 01:47:42,699
[SPEAKER_01] A kako su dolazili ovi,

3155
01:47:42,699 --> 01:47:44,680
[SPEAKER_01] a što je i dalje ona

3156
01:47:44,680 --> 01:47:47,020
[SPEAKER_01] u neokolonialnom sustavu,

3157
01:47:47,020 --> 01:47:48,699
[SPEAKER_01] pa su joj sad i sjeravaju vani,

3158
01:47:48,699 --> 01:47:51,340
[SPEAKER_01] jer je dosta njima kolonializma

3159
01:47:51,340 --> 01:47:52,760
[SPEAKER_01] ili svega što ima.

3160
01:47:52,760 --> 01:47:54,100
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, svijet se promjenjiva,

3161
01:47:54,100 --> 01:47:54,680
[SPEAKER_01] tebala.

3162
01:47:55,560 --> 01:47:58,640
[SPEAKER_01] Naravno da ima tih rubnih dijelova,

3163
01:47:58,640 --> 01:48:01,840
[SPEAKER_01] a Hrvatska pripada tom rubnom dijelu,

3164
01:48:01,840 --> 01:48:03,960
[SPEAKER_01] gdje može biti u ovome slučaju,

3165
01:48:03,960 --> 01:48:05,260
[SPEAKER_01] može biti na zapadu

3166
01:48:05,260 --> 01:48:07,460
[SPEAKER_01] i može biti na istoku.

3167
01:48:07,460 --> 01:48:11,079
[SPEAKER_01] Ali, Hrvatska ima jednu jedinu točku

3168
01:48:11,079 --> 01:48:13,079
[SPEAKER_01] u Evropi, nema ništa,

3169
01:48:13,079 --> 01:48:14,340
[SPEAKER_01] zato moji dragi gledatelji,

3170
01:48:14,340 --> 01:48:15,520
[SPEAKER_01] razumijete ovo čemu govorim,

3171
01:48:15,520 --> 01:48:16,479
[SPEAKER_01] toga je bio svjestan

3172
01:48:16,479 --> 01:48:18,479
[SPEAKER_01] naš predsjednik Tužban,

3173
01:48:18,479 --> 01:48:20,479
[SPEAKER_01] pa je onda išao u sve zemlje

3174
01:48:20,479 --> 01:48:22,420
[SPEAKER_01] da bi napravio Hrvatsko državu

3175
01:48:22,420 --> 01:48:23,060
[SPEAKER_01] i obranio.

3176
01:48:23,060 --> 01:48:26,500
[SPEAKER_01] To je takozvana četvrta gravitacijska

3177
01:48:26,500 --> 01:48:27,380
[SPEAKER_01] stožena točka.

3178
01:48:27,380 --> 01:48:28,960
[SPEAKER_01] Ima četiri u Evropi,

3179
01:48:28,960 --> 01:48:30,619
[SPEAKER_01] zapravo sedamnaest i u svijetu ima.

3180
01:48:30,619 --> 01:48:33,020
[SPEAKER_01] Toko najvišće razine je geostrategije.

3181
01:48:33,020 --> 01:48:35,199
[SPEAKER_01] Ona je spoj, kopna i mora.

3182
01:48:35,199 --> 01:48:37,979
[SPEAKER_01] I četiri su Evropi,

3183
01:48:37,979 --> 01:48:39,239
[SPEAKER_01] La Manche, Gibratar,

3184
01:48:39,239 --> 01:48:41,640
[SPEAKER_01] Bospod Danenele i Orthrad Jadran.

3185
01:48:41,640 --> 01:48:43,060
[SPEAKER_01] A Jadran je dvije trećine naše.

3186
01:48:43,060 --> 01:48:45,180
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, mi se nalazimo na gravitacijsku točku.

3187
01:48:46,479 --> 01:48:48,260
[SPEAKER_01] Tu se prelamaju

3188
01:48:48,260 --> 01:48:51,180
[SPEAKER_01] utjecaj velikog tabora,

3189
01:48:51,180 --> 01:48:52,239
[SPEAKER_01] aglosaksonskog,

3190
01:48:52,239 --> 01:48:53,539
[SPEAKER_01] ili Amerike u podučnosti,

3191
01:48:53,539 --> 01:48:54,819
[SPEAKER_01] i ruskog.

3192
01:48:54,819 --> 01:48:57,020
[SPEAKER_01] Ali tu je i kineski,

3193
01:48:57,020 --> 01:48:59,180
[SPEAKER_01] jer kineski novi put svigle

3194
01:48:59,180 --> 01:49:01,260
[SPEAKER_01] ili kineska geopolitika

3195
01:49:01,260 --> 01:49:03,479
[SPEAKER_01] završava u Savudrijskoj vali,

3196
01:49:03,479 --> 01:49:04,619
[SPEAKER_01] u rijeci.

3197
01:49:04,619 --> 01:49:06,039
[SPEAKER_01] Zato su kinezi gradili

3198
01:49:06,039 --> 01:49:07,680
[SPEAKER_01] onaj most infrastrukturno.

3199
01:49:07,680 --> 01:49:09,399
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, na našem prostoru

3200
01:49:09,399 --> 01:49:12,279
[SPEAKER_01] se sučeljaju sve tri velika tabora.

3201
01:49:12,279 --> 01:49:14,220
[SPEAKER_01] Prema tome,

3202
01:49:14,220 --> 01:49:16,119
[SPEAKER_01] isprana geopolitika Hrvatska

3203
01:49:16,119 --> 01:49:16,840
[SPEAKER_01] bi bila ova.

3204
01:49:16,840 --> 01:49:19,159
[SPEAKER_01] Voditi sa svima

3205
01:49:19,159 --> 01:49:19,899
[SPEAKER_01] razgovore,

3206
01:49:19,899 --> 01:49:21,960
[SPEAKER_01] a ne se opredijeliti

3207
01:49:21,960 --> 01:49:23,020
[SPEAKER_01] za jednu stranu,

3208
01:49:23,020 --> 01:49:25,539
[SPEAKER_01] jer niko vam ne može jamčiti

3209
01:49:25,539 --> 01:49:27,399
[SPEAKER_01] da će ta strana

3210
01:49:27,399 --> 01:49:28,359
[SPEAKER_01] za koju se opredijeli

3211
01:49:28,359 --> 01:49:29,720
[SPEAKER_01] sutra u istinu biti

3212
01:49:29,720 --> 01:49:31,260
[SPEAKER_01] glavni igraž.

3213
01:49:31,260 --> 01:49:32,119
[SPEAKER_01] Odnosno,

3214
01:49:32,119 --> 01:49:33,340
[SPEAKER_01] čak neopne.

3215
01:49:33,340 --> 01:49:34,899
[SPEAKER_01] Jer svaki imperiju,

3216
01:49:34,899 --> 01:49:37,020
[SPEAKER_01] kao što je rimski propao,

3217
01:49:37,020 --> 01:49:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] tako će i propasti

3218
01:49:38,000 --> 01:49:39,460
[SPEAKER_01] i američki imperiju.

3219
01:49:39,460 --> 01:49:40,739
[SPEAKER_01] On već sad da se urušava.

3220
01:49:40,739 --> 01:49:42,300
[SPEAKER_01] Ona je urušavao se

3221
01:49:42,300 --> 01:49:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] dvijesta godina.

3222
01:49:43,000 --> 01:49:43,960
[SPEAKER_01] ovaj će možda, recimo,

3223
01:49:43,960 --> 01:49:45,220
[SPEAKER_01] 50 ili 100 godina.

3224
01:49:45,220 --> 01:49:46,539
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ne možete jamčiti.

3225
01:49:46,920 --> 01:49:47,479
[SPEAKER_01] politika,

3226
01:49:47,479 --> 01:49:48,399
[SPEAKER_01] kad se ti nalažiš

3227
01:49:48,399 --> 01:49:49,520
[SPEAKER_01] na garantijskoj točki,

3228
01:49:49,520 --> 01:49:51,199
[SPEAKER_01] ne smiješ se opredijeliti

3229
01:49:51,199 --> 01:49:52,020
[SPEAKER_01] za jednu stranu,

3230
01:49:52,020 --> 01:49:53,180
[SPEAKER_01] nego igrati sa svima.

3231
01:49:53,180 --> 01:49:54,460
[SPEAKER_01] Znaš koji je to bije

3232
01:49:54,460 --> 01:49:55,140
[SPEAKER_01] najpametniji?

3233
01:49:55,140 --> 01:49:56,979
[SPEAKER_01] Dubrovončani,

3234
01:49:56,979 --> 01:49:57,920
[SPEAKER_01] stariji,

3235
01:49:57,920 --> 01:49:58,720
[SPEAKER_01] poklisari.

3236
01:49:59,520 --> 01:50:00,899
[SPEAKER_01] E, sa svima dobro,

3237
01:50:00,899 --> 01:50:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] ali slikim iskreno.

3238
01:50:02,000 --> 01:50:02,800
[SPEAKER_00] A svoje,

3239
01:50:02,800 --> 01:50:04,300
[SPEAKER_00] ali svoje radiš i vodijš.

3240
01:50:04,300 --> 01:50:05,020
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim svoje.

3241
01:50:05,020 --> 01:50:06,220
[SPEAKER_00] Sjajna poruka,

3242
01:50:06,220 --> 01:50:06,720
[SPEAKER_00] admirale,

3243
01:50:06,720 --> 01:50:07,100
[SPEAKER_00] za kraj.

3244
01:50:07,100 --> 01:50:07,739
[SPEAKER_00] Nadam se da smo

3245
01:50:07,739 --> 01:50:08,920
[SPEAKER_00] našim slušateljima

3246
01:50:08,920 --> 01:50:10,159
[SPEAKER_00] i gledateljima

3247
01:50:10,159 --> 01:50:10,680
[SPEAKER_00] prije svega

3248
01:50:10,680 --> 01:50:13,220
[SPEAKER_00] utažili glad

3249
01:50:13,220 --> 01:50:14,579
[SPEAKER_00] za novim informacijama,

3250
01:50:14,579 --> 01:50:16,020
[SPEAKER_00] komentarima i analizama,

3251
01:50:16,020 --> 01:50:16,539
[SPEAKER_00] a doista,

3252
01:50:16,539 --> 01:50:17,420
[SPEAKER_00] evo,

3253
01:50:17,420 --> 01:50:18,300
[SPEAKER_00] mislim da smo

3254
01:50:18,300 --> 01:50:19,739
[SPEAKER_00] dosta toga dotakli.

3255
01:50:19,739 --> 01:50:21,420
[SPEAKER_01] A jesmo dosta toga dotakli.

3256
01:50:21,420 --> 01:50:23,159
[SPEAKER_01] Ovo ga bilo je zanimljivo

3257
01:50:23,159 --> 01:50:24,399
[SPEAKER_01] nakon tako šest mjeseci.

3258
01:50:24,399 --> 01:50:24,819
[SPEAKER_01] A da.

3259
01:50:24,859 --> 01:50:25,460
[SPEAKER_01] bar se nadamo

3260
01:50:25,460 --> 01:50:26,800
[SPEAKER_01] da nećemo još šest mjeseci

3261
01:50:26,800 --> 01:50:27,260
[SPEAKER_01] cekati.

3262
01:50:27,260 --> 01:50:27,680
[SPEAKER_01] Ok.

3263
01:50:27,680 --> 01:50:29,199
[SPEAKER_01] Jer se procesi ubrzavaju.

3264
01:50:29,199 --> 01:50:30,479
[SPEAKER_00] Procesi se ubrzavaju,

3265
01:50:30,479 --> 01:50:32,300
[SPEAKER_00] a prvi pa lošo,

3266
01:50:32,300 --> 01:50:33,899
[SPEAKER_00] nek bude kako treba.

3267
01:50:33,899 --> 01:50:34,600
[SPEAKER_00] Može tako.

3268
01:50:34,600 --> 01:50:35,899
[SPEAKER_00] Hvala vam najljepša,

3269
01:50:35,899 --> 01:50:36,319
[SPEAKER_00] admirale.

3270
01:50:36,319 --> 01:50:36,640
[SPEAKER_00] Hvala vam.

3271
01:50:36,640 --> 01:50:38,500
[SPEAKER_00] Bio je ovo podcast Mrežnica

3272
01:50:38,500 --> 01:50:39,140
[SPEAKER_00] naš gost,

3273
01:50:39,140 --> 01:50:41,060
[SPEAKER_00] admiral Davor Domazet Lošo.

3274
01:50:41,060 --> 01:50:42,800
[SPEAKER_00] Hvala vam svima na pozornosti.

3275
01:50:42,800 --> 01:50:43,800
[SPEAKER_00] Vidimo se naravno

3276
01:50:43,800 --> 01:50:44,539
[SPEAKER_00] vrlo brzo.

